      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBp7jgeQQHtp47fNGdiglZdlL_zAevzOPhalTNmIkMO0oG5yyQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a month ago",
      "text": "Service was AMAZING! I hired them to paint my new salon suite. Communication was top tier. They color matched to my specifications beautifully. Scheduling was very flexible and they were able to work around some unforseen hiccups on my end.  It was over all very well done with care and love and I absolutely will be recommending them out for future projects!",
      "time": 1779592243,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
