      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a month ago",
      "text": "Bridgette and Skylie painted my bedroom and it looks beautiful! They showed up on time, they were quick, clean, detailed and reasonably priced. I highly recommend them to anyone who may need painting done in their home! 5 stars all the way!!",
